{"tid":846931,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"香港有縱深　二戰日軍侵港　打足18日","createTime":"2018-10-03T19:44:54.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-04T06:39:10.000Z","uid":47714,"like":7,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"539c1cc73092479c12cbf380172c56d00942fd36","tid":846931,"uid":47714,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-03T19:44:54.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/TaiwaneseLocalismFront/posts/571503736544069\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2FTaiwaneseLocalismFront%2Fposts%2F571503736544069&d=1mmyXRMGVbxG6j%2BI44FLDS7bS0i5kAixZS1hjGmvpwM%3D&h=99c824dc\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/TaiwaneseLocalismFront/posts/571503736544069</a><br />\n<br />\nSian Lo Lung:<br />\n<br />\n戰略縱深的部份，我的計法是基於時間成本上的距離。<br />\n<br />\n多高山，多島嶼，少平地，地形曲折，形成的是推進緩慢受阻，二戰時的香港保衛戰就打了十八日。生活在香港也能感受到這點，香港雖小，但交通成本昂貴和耗時，且極容易擠塞。地面進攻的話，北方來的中國軍隊除非能穿透而無視山岳和水上步行，否則也是會受阻。<br />\n<br />\n撤退無疑是一個問題，香港軍撤退，是要撤退到海外。戰爭時需要立即在海外成立臨時司令部，從海外奪回香港。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/HK.NationFront/posts/2078379585737074\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2FHK.NationFront%2Fposts%2F2078379585737074&d=1mmyXRMGVbxG6j%2BI44FLDS7bS0i5kAixZS1hjGmvpwM%3D&h=c0ff2e9b\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/HK.NationFront/posts/2078379585737074</a><br />\n<br />\n香港民族陣綫:<br />\n<br />\n直至1995年之前，香港都有一支主要由香港人編成的軍隊，叫皇家香港軍團(或者叫義勇軍)。由於呢支部隊直屬香港政府而唔係英國政府，所以二戰歐洲打到火紅火綠都好，都冇調離香港。<br />\n<br />\n1941年12月，香港防衛軍動員2,200名各級團員參加香港保衛戰，合計289名團員殉職或者失蹤，到12月26日，佢地係全港最後一批投降的部隊。投降後，部分團員去左緬甸組成香港義勇軍連，繼續作戰。一些團員則在中國組成英軍服務團，協助中國政府作戰，主要為盟軍收集情報及營救工作。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://pbs.twimg.com/media/Dbous-GUQAIqsPH.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpbs.twimg.com%2Fmedia%2FDbous-GUQAIqsPH.jpg&h=6880ab39&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"14236b9e42be8930af5287b7946f0f387f18bb38","tid":846931,"uid":156363,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-03T20:37:23.000Z","msg":"二戰新界連馬路都唔多條，宜家2粒鐘唔駛就全部淪陷啦。"},{"pid":"a2b4eccaed6998cb48d315a6dc257abc5c03f0bd","tid":846931,"uid":191815,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-03T22:40:25.000Z","msg":"97解放軍入侵 打足廿年 飛機"},{"pid":"2f268af0a88fcdf6e6f8626ba2e62e902b6ddeaa","tid":846931,"uid":48234,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a2b4eccaed6998cb48d315a6dc257abc5c03f0bd","tid":846931,"uid":191815,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-03T22:40:25.000Z","msg":"97解放軍入侵 打足廿年 飛機"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-03T22:41:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7a5e14c1f02cfedcde375acc515da2e464cbfa2d","tid":846931,"uid":158270,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-04T06:39:10.000Z","msg":"That's why起高鐵"}]}